    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably every time, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, ensuring a comfortable driving experience. While there are some minor signs of cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the car is mechanically sound and ready for daily use. Prospective buyers can expect a dependable vehicle that has been cared for with regular service intervals.",
