    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a solid option for someone looking for a reliable driver at a reasonable price. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows clear signs of use, including some staining on the upholstery and wear on the steering wheel. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it will likely need a routine service and new tires in the near future. It is a functional, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price of a newer model.",
