    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the most exacting standards. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar in pristine, showroom condition. Every surface and mechanical component reflects meticulous preservation, offering an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector. Its aesthetic and functional integrity are absolute.",
